godina nee biti izuzetak.

9
00:01:25,065 --> 00:01:26,896
Izvoli, knedlice.

10
00:01:26,933 --> 00:01:28,560
Moja mama

11
00:01:28,602 --> 00:01:30,001
je udno stvorenje
iz vremena

12
00:01:30,036 --> 00:01:31,367
kada su akalice

13
00:01:31,405 --> 00:01:32,895
jo uvek bile oznaka
visokog ugleda.

14
00:01:32,939 --> 00:01:34,566
Podmetai, Pam?
Zdravo, Bridit.

15
00:01:34,608 --> 00:01:36,735
Trea fioka od vrha, Una.

16
00:01:36,777 --> 00:01:38,745
Ispod krastavia.

17
00:01:38,745 --> 00:01:42,977
Usput, Darsijevi su tu.
Doveli su i Marka.

18
00:01:43,016 --> 00:01:44,574
Ah, poinje.

19
00:01:44,618 --> 00:01:46,017
Seas se Marka.

20
00:01:46,052 --> 00:01:47,713
Igrali ste se u
njegovom bazenu.

21
00:01:47,754 --> 00:01:49,589
On je advokat.
Vrlo imuan.

22
00:01:49,589 --> 00:01:51,648
Ne, ne seam se.

23
00:01:51,691 --> 00:01:53,591
Razveden je, oigledno.

24
00:01:53,627 --> 00:01:56,095
ena mu je bila Japanka.
Vrlo okrutna rasa.

25
00:01:56,129 --> 00:01:57,790
Nego ta e obui?

26
00:01:57,831 --> 00:01:58,957
Ovo.

27
00:01:58,999 --> 00:02:00,899
Ne budi smena,
Bridit.

28
00:02:00,934 --> 00:02:02,060
Nikad nee nai deka

29
00:02:02,102 --> 00:02:04,070
ako izgleda
kao da si izala iz Auvica.

30
00:02:04,104 --> 00:02:05,093
Idi sad gore.

31
00:02:05,138 --> 00:02:07,107
Ostavila sam ti neto
ljupko na krevetu.

32
00:02:16,650 --> 00:02:21,019
Divno.
Nosila sam tepih.

33
00:02:21,054 --> 00:02:22,885
Eto nje.

34
00:02:22,923 --> 00:02:26,882
Moja mala Bridit.

35
00:02:26,927 --> 00:02:29,418
Zdravo, ujka Defri. 

36
00:02:29,463 --> 00:02:30,760
Jesi li popila neto?
-Ne.

37
00:02:30,797 --> 00:02:32,059
Ne? Hajde onda.

38
00:02:32,098 --> 00:02:33,793
U stvari, nije mi ujak.

39
00:02:33,834 --> 00:02:35,597
Neko ko insistira
da ga nazivam ujakom,

40
00:02:35,635 --> 00:02:36,966
dok me hvata za zadnjicu

41
00:02:37,003 --> 00:02:40,097
i postavlja mi strana pitanja.

42
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:43,166
Kako ljubavni ivot?

43
00:02:43,210 --> 00:02:45,440
Super. Hvala, ujko.

44
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:47,481
Jo si bez deka?
Ne znam.

45
00:02:47,481 --> 00:02:49,972
Vi to jurite  karijeru.
Ne moete zauvek to da odlaete.

46
00:02:50,016 --> 00:02:51,916
Tik-tak, tik-tak.

47
00:02:51,952 --> 00:02:54,477
Zdravo, tata.
-Zdravo, duo.

48
00:02:54,521 --> 00:02:56,079
Kako je?

49
00:02:56,122 --> 00:02:57,714
Muno.

50
00:02:57,757 --> 00:03:00,658
Majka pokuava da ti namesti
nekog razvedenog.

51
00:03:02,128 --> 00:03:05,188
Advokat za ljudska prava.
Oigledno, opaka zverka.

52
00:03:05,232 --> 00:03:08,668
Hu. Ding-dong.

53
00:03:08,702 --> 00:03:11,535
Moda je mama ovaj put uspela.

54
00:03:11,571 --> 00:03:14,904
Hajde. Da vidimo da li je
Mark za pie?

55
00:03:14,941 --> 00:03:16,932
Sreno.

56
00:03:17,010 --> 00:03:18,500
Mark?

57
00:03:18,545 --> 00:03:21,241
Moda je ovo taj tajanstveni
gospodin Pravi

58
00:03:21,281 --> 00:03:24,079
na koga ekam celog ivota.

59
00:03:24,117 --> 00:03:27,177
Sea se Bridit.

60
00:03:27,220 --> 00:03:28,983
Moda i ne.

61
00:03:29,022 --> 00:03:30,785
Trala je po tvom travnjaku

62
00:03:30,824 --> 00:03:32,985
bez odee, sea se?

63
00:03:33,026 --> 00:03:35,085
Ne, ne ba tako.

64
00:03:36,796 --> 00:03:37,990
Idi proveri sos, Pam.

65
00:03:38,031 --> 00:03:39,896
Izgleda da treba da ga procedi.

66
00:03:39,933 --> 00:03:41,127
Naravno da ne treba.

67
00:03:41,167 --> 00:03:42,930
Samo ga promeaj, Una.

68
00:03:44,704 --> 00:03:46,171
Da, naravno.
Odmah dolazim.

69
00:03:46,206 --> 00:03:49,175
Izvinite. Zove me zgruani sos.

70
00:03:53,179 --> 00:03:56,148
-Pa...
-Pa...

71
00:03:56,182 --> 00:03:59,310
Ostaje sa roditeljima za
Novu Godinu?

72
00:03:59,519 --> 00:04:00,884
-Da.

73
00:04:00,921 --> 00:04:02,320
Ti?
-Oh, ne, ne, ne.

74
00:04:02,522 --> 00:04:04,513
Bila sam sino u Londonu
na urci

75
00:04:04,558 --> 00:04:06,856
i bojim se da sam
jo mamurna.

76
00:04:06,893 --> 00:04:08,827
Volela bih da zaglavim glavu
u toaletsku olju

77
00:04:08,862 --> 00:04:10,329
kao sav normalan svet.

78
00:04:12,332 --> 00:04:15,028
Novogodinja odluka
manje pia.

79
00:04:15,068 --> 00:04:18,037
Oh i prestani da pui.

80
00:04:18,071 --> 00:04:20,733
Oh.
-Oh. 

81
00:04:20,774 --> 00:04:23,174
I dri se novogodinjih odluka.

82
00:04:24,945 --> 00:04:27,914
Oh. I...

83
00:04:27,914 --> 00:04:30,883
prekini da pria
budalatine strancima.

84
00:04:30,917 --> 00:04:33,219
U stvari, prestani
da pria, taka.

85
00:04:33,219 --> 00:04:36,814
Pa, onda,
moda je vreme za jelo.

86
00:04:39,693 --> 00:04:40,625
Oigledno...

87
00:04:41,595 --> 00:04:42,721
je da ivi tu odmah
iza oka od tebe.

88
00:04:42,762 --> 00:04:45,322
Majko, ne treba mi sudar na slepo.

89
00:04:45,365 --> 00:04:47,993
Naroitio ne sa nekom
nedoreenom zagorelom osobom

90
00:04:48,034 --> 00:04:49,797
koja se pui kao dimnjak,
pije kao riba

91
00:04:49,836 --> 00:04:51,895
i oblai kao majka.

92
00:04:54,574 --> 00:04:56,269
Ukusno.

93
00:04:56,309 --> 00:04:58,174
urka sa karijem.

94
00:04:58,211 --> 00:05:00,076
Moje omiljeno.

95
00:05:00,113 --> 00:05:02,946
I to je bilo to.
Ba tada.

96
00:05:02,983 --> 00:05:05,918
Ba tada.
To je bio trenutak.

97
00:05:08,121 --> 00:05:11,318
Iznenada sam shvatila da ako se
neto iznenada ne promeni

98
00:05:11,358 --> 00:05:14,020
da u proiveti ivot sa
jedinom stalnom vezom

99
00:05:14,060 --> 00:05:15,925
u vidu vinske boce

100
00:05:15,962 --> 00:05:19,125
i da u konano umreti
debela i usamljena

101
00:05:19,165 --> 00:05:22,965
i da e me nai posle 3 nedelje,
polu pojedenu od strane divljih pasa.

102
00:05:23,003 --> 00:05:25,631
Orl je trebalo da se
pretvori u Glen Klouz

103
00:05:25,672 --> 00:05:27,105
u "Fatalnoj privlanosti."

104
00:05:28,708 --> 00:05:34,977
Potpuno sama.

105
00:05:35,015 --> 00:05:36,949
Ne elim da budem

106
00:05:36,983 --> 00:05:41,321
potpuno sama.

107
00:05:44,357 --> 00:05:46,951
Nemate poruka.

108
00:06:13,286 --> 00:06:15,186
Kada sam bila mlada

109
00:06:16,756 --> 00:06:20,157
nisam trebala nikoga

110
00:06:22,862 --> 00:06:26,457
a ljubav mi je bila samo zabava.

111
00:06:28,802 --> 00:06:31,327
Ti dani su proli.

112
00:06:36,710 --> 00:06:41,704
Potpuno sama

113
00:06:42,882 --> 00:06:44,474
ne elim da budem

114
00:06:44,684 --> 00:06:49,053
potpuno sama.

115
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:15,771
Potpuno sama.

116
00:07:16,816 --> 00:07:19,979
Ne elim da ivim...

117
00:07:20,019 --> 00:07:22,044
I tako sam donela vanu odluku.

118
00:07:22,088 --> 00:07:23,487
Morala sam da se
obezbedim

119
00:07:23,523 --> 00:07:26,788
da ne bih zavrila smuene face
sluajui na radiju

120
00:07:26,826 --> 00:07:29,260
tune lagere za one
preko trideset.

121
00:07:29,295 --> 00:07:32,230
Reila sam da uzmem
ivot u svoje ruke

122
00:07:32,265 --> 00:07:33,755
i ponem dnevnik

123
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:36,462
da bih ispriala istinu
o Bridit Dons,

124
00:07:36,503 --> 00:07:37,868
celu istinu.

125
00:07:39,272 --> 00:07:41,399
Odluka broj 1.

126
00:07:42,275 --> 00:07:43,243
Oigledno treba da smram
10 kilograma.

127
00:07:43,243 --> 00:07:44,141
Broj 2.

128
00:07:44,177 --> 00:07:46,737
Uvek ostavi gaice od sino
u korpu za ve.

129
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,145
Jednako vano,

130
00:07:48,181 --> 00:07:50,809
nai u razumnog deka
za izlaske

131
00:07:50,850 --> 00:07:52,875
i neu nastaviti da stvaram
romantine veze

132
00:07:52,919 --> 00:07:54,409
ni sa jednim od sledeih:

133
00:07:54,454 --> 00:07:56,820
alkoholiarima, karijeristima,
uplaenima od veze,

134
00:07:56,856 --> 00:07:58,187
voajerima, megalomanijacima,

135
00:07:58,224 --> 00:08:00,124
emotivno sjebanim
ili sa perverznjacima.

136
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:02,856
A naroito neu
da matam

137
00:08:02,896 --> 00:08:07,424
o nekoj osobi koja je
otelotvorenje svega toga.

138
00:08:07,467 --> 00:08:10,527
Ono to eli.

139
00:08:10,770 --> 00:08:12,863
Duo,ja imam

140
00:08:12,906 --> 00:08:14,567
ono to ti treba.

141
00:08:14,774 --> 00:08:16,173
Zna li da imam?

142
00:08:16,209 --> 00:08:19,576
Na nesreu, on mi je sasvim
sluajno ef.

143
00:08:19,813 --> 00:08:21,838
Glavni urednik, Daniel Kliver.

144
00:08:21,881 --> 00:08:23,783
A iz raznih pomalo
nepravednih razloga

145
00:08:23,783 --> 00:08:26,013
u vezi sa boinom zabavom

146
00:08:26,052 --> 00:08:29,920
pretpostavljam da on
o meni ne mata.

147
00:08:32,125 --> 00:08:36,255
Ne mogu da ivim

148
00:08:36,296 --> 00:08:39,959
ako to moram bez tebe.

149
00:08:39,999 --> 00:08:44,561
Ne mogu da ivim.

150
00:08:44,604 --> 00:08:46,231
Ne mogu vie da dajem.

151
00:08:46,272 --> 00:08:48,797
Ili moda greim.

152
00:09:00,486 --> 00:09:02,818
Srena Nova, gospodine Ficarbert.

153
00:09:02,856 --> 00:09:04,187
Srena Nova, Brenda.

154
00:09:04,224 --> 00:09:06,920
Gospodin Ficarbert,
vie lii na perverznjaka.

155
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,825
Danielov ef koji slobodno
bulji u moje grudi,

156
00:09:08,862 --> 00:09:11,626
a da nema pojma ko sam
ili ta radim.

157
00:09:11,831 --> 00:09:13,992
Dobro jutro. Potrebno mi je to
"Kafkin Motor" izdanje

158
00:09:14,033 --> 00:09:15,193
do 11:00.

159
00:09:15,235 --> 00:09:17,863
Perpetua, neto starija

160
00:09:17,904 --> 00:09:19,929
i zato smatra
da uvek upravlja samnom.

161
00:09:19,973 --> 00:09:21,133
Vei deo vremena

162
00:09:21,174 --> 00:09:23,836
razmiljam da joj napunim
glavu spajalicama.

163
00:09:25,078 --> 00:09:26,238
Publicitet.

164
00:09:26,279 --> 00:09:28,213
Sve to sam traila...
Samo sam pitala...

165
00:09:28,248 --> 00:09:31,012
da li eli da doe na mali
odmor u Pariz.

166
00:09:31,050 --> 00:09:33,018
Dnevni poziv od Dud.
Najbolja drugarica.

167
00:09:33,052 --> 00:09:34,986
Vodea za investicije
u Brajtlings banci,

168
00:09:35,021 --> 00:09:36,545
a provodi vei deo vremena

169
00:09:36,589 --> 00:09:39,456
zarobljena u toaletu,
plaui zbog svog sjebanog deka.

170
00:09:39,492 --> 00:09:41,084
Isuvie traim.

171
00:09:41,127 --> 00:09:42,651
Zar ne mogu bez uzora?

172
00:09:42,862 --> 00:09:44,227
Ma moe.

173
00:09:44,264 --> 00:09:46,357
To nije za tebe.
Ti si ljupka.

174
00:09:46,399 --> 00:09:48,333
To je Vil Riard.

175
00:09:48,368 --> 00:09:51,269
On je  samo ogromna brava
bez kvake.

176
00:09:53,206 --> 00:09:57,609
Takvo je miljenje nekih
o Kafki,

177
00:09:57,644 --> 00:09:59,578
ali oni silno gree.

178
00:09:59,612 --> 00:10:01,136
Ova knjiga predstavlja
uzbuujuu viziju

179
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:03,273
rana koje je ovaj
vek zadao

180
00:10:03,316 --> 00:10:05,218
tradicionalnoj mukosti.

181
00:10:05,218 --> 00:10:08,244
Ona je pozitivno
voneguteska.

182
00:10:08,288 --> 00:10:10,256
Hvala to ste zvali,
profesore Lives.

183
00:10:11,557 --> 00:10:14,355
Lista gostiju za prijem.

184
00:10:17,096 --> 00:10:20,497
ta znai F.R. Lives?

185
00:10:25,605 --> 00:10:27,334
Onaj F.R. Lives

186
00:10:27,373 --> 00:10:30,069
koji je napisao "Civilzacija mase
i kultura manjina"?

187
00:10:31,644 --> 00:10:35,375
Onaj F.R. Lives
to je umro 1978?

188
00:10:38,384 --> 00:10:40,215
Zapanjujue.

189
00:10:42,922 --> 00:10:44,685
Hitan sastanak
sa urbanom porodicom

190
00:10:44,724 --> 00:10:47,124
radi koherentne diskusije
o krizi karijere.

191
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:49,424
Neka se nose.
Neka se svi nose.

192
00:10:49,462 --> 00:10:51,521
Kai im da mogu da zabiju
jebenog Livesa

193
00:10:51,597 --> 00:10:53,394
u njihove jebene guzice.

194
00:10:53,433 --> 00:10:56,027
Dobro, dobro.
To je vrlo, vrlo korisno.

195
00:10:56,069 --> 00:10:57,536
Novinar azer,

196
00:10:57,570 --> 00:10:59,401
koji voli puno da
upotrebljava re jebanje.

197
00:10:59,439 --> 00:11:01,999
A ta bi ti uradila, Dud,
da je neko od tvojih asistenata

198
00:11:02,041 --> 00:11:04,271
napravio tako malu i
beznaajnu greku?

199
00:11:04,310 --> 00:11:05,641
Otpustila bih te, Brid.

200
00:11:05,678 --> 00:11:07,407
Odlino.

201
00:11:07,447 --> 00:11:09,642
Je li onaj Kliver
jo uvek onako sladak?

202
00:11:09,682 --> 00:11:11,115
Oh, Boe, jeste.

203
00:11:11,150 --> 00:11:13,119
Onda mislim da bi
pravovremeni felacio

204
00:11:13,119 --> 00:11:14,245
bio najbolji odgovor.

205
00:11:14,287 --> 00:11:15,618
Oh, svia ti se.

206
00:11:15,655 --> 00:11:17,953
Jesi li ti onaj koji je pevao onu pesmu?

207
00:11:17,991 --> 00:11:19,686
Da, da, jesam.

208
00:11:19,726 --> 00:11:21,421
Tom, pop ikona osamdesetih

209
00:11:21,461 --> 00:11:23,554
koji je imao samo jednu
hit plou,

210
00:11:23,596 --> 00:11:25,530
a onda se povukao jer je skapirao
da mu je ta jedna ploa

211
00:11:25,565 --> 00:11:27,032
sasvim dovoljna da
povali neto

212
00:11:27,066 --> 00:11:28,556
kroz cele devedesete.

213
00:11:28,601 --> 00:11:31,229
Odlina pesma.
-Veliko vam hvala.

214
00:11:31,270 --> 00:11:32,638
ista ljiga, naravno.

215
00:11:32,638 --> 00:11:34,640
Jo votke?
-Ne.

216
00:11:34,640 --> 00:11:37,541
Da.
Do vrha, doavola.

217
00:11:37,577 --> 00:11:39,204
Bar sad kada sam
u tridesetim

218
00:11:39,245 --> 00:11:40,439
mogu da podnesem pie.

219
00:11:44,384 --> 00:11:47,649
Pazi gde staje.
-Dobro je. Vozi dalje.

220
00:11:48,021 --> 00:11:52,287
Izgleda da
F.R. Lives dolazi.

221
00:11:54,260 --> 00:11:56,285
Dobar dan, Bridit.

222
00:11:56,362 --> 00:11:59,456
Kako to misli
ide na odmor?

223
00:11:59,499 --> 00:12:02,400
A ta sa Duliom?

224
00:12:04,504 --> 00:12:07,667
Da li mora da
ide na sahranu?

225
00:12:32,031 --> 00:12:34,591
Sluaj, imamo mali problem.

226
00:12:36,536 --> 00:12:39,528
Jedini problem je u kuhinji.

227
00:12:39,572 --> 00:12:41,506
Iskreno, nema mesta...

228
00:12:41,541 --> 00:12:44,635
Poruka gospodin Kliver.

229
00:12:44,677 --> 00:12:47,202
Uasnuta sam porukom.

230
00:12:47,246 --> 00:12:51,239
Suknja je iz protesta,
ni bolesna ni odsutna.

231
00:12:51,284 --> 00:12:54,344
Privuena bukvalnom veliinom
uprave je stav prema

232
00:12:54,387 --> 00:12:55,581
haljini.

233
00:12:55,621 --> 00:12:59,318
Predlaem da je uprava bolesna,
ne suknja!

234
00:12:59,358 --> 00:13:01,326
To je glupost.

235
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,521
 Oh, shvatam.

236
00:13:03,563 --> 00:13:05,258
Stani malo.

237
00:13:12,405 --> 00:13:14,873
Tako je. 

238
00:13:15,074 --> 00:13:16,803
